data.description: This immaculately kept 5BR/3BA/2HalfBath and a bonus room home has almost too much to list. Everything is maintained and cared for. Beautifully decorated with lots of extras that include an add'l freezer and refrigerator, security system that can be transferred to new owners, 4 TV's, 12x16 hardy board built shop, very large screened pool, two add'l covered areas for lawn mower etc.and fish cleaning area. Brand new A/C, roof is 3 yrs old and pool liner 3 yrs old. AMPLE Storage and then some. This is a furnished TURN KEY home that's ready to move in.
